==English==

===Verb===
'''[[back]] [[up]]''' 
# (''intransitive'') {{Cricket}} For the [[non striker]] to take a few [[step]]s down the [[pitch]], in [[preparation]] to taking a [[run]], just as the [[bowler]] [[bowl]]s the [[ball]].
# (''intrastitive'') {{Cricket}} For a [[fielder]] to [[position]] [[himself]] behind the [[wicket]] (relative to a team-mate who is [[throw]]ing the ball at the wicket) so as to stop the ball, and [[prevent]] [[overthrow]]s.

